=Description=

"Coopcycle is an international federation of cooperatives. Anyone can start their own bicycle courier cooperative, become a member of the federation, then get use of the software and have a say in the features they'd like to see incorporated into the platform. It's then up to the individual cooperatives to engage with businesses, provide sustainable work for their members, etc."

